> wrong key anyway.
> 
> But before I go off and pay a lock smith to make me some new keys, I decided
> it would be a good idea to check and make sure that this actually is the
> case... in other words, do the old VWs use two different keys for unlocking
> the doors and starting the ignition?  Also, I'm considering just taking it
> to a VW shop and asking them to completely replace _all_ of the locks for me
